---
---
<section class="huddle section-dark">
  <div class="container huddle-inner">
    <div class="huddle-copy">
      <span class="huddle-badge">First Live Q&amp;A &middot; Aug 4 @ 7pm</span>
      <p class="eyebrow">The Spit-Up Society</p>
      <h2>Fatherhood was never supposed to be a solo sport.</h2>
      <p class="huddle-sub">
        Bring your real questions to John and Mike, live — pregnancy, birth, the newborn
        blur, marriage after baby. Join before August 4th and you're in: we'll email you the
        link.
      </p>
      <ul class="huddle-list">
        <li>Weekly Huddles</li>
        <li>Live Q&amp;A, twice a month</li>
        <li>Private Community</li>
        <li>Sleep Support</li>
        <li>Early access to merch &amp; guides</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="huddle-price">
        <span class="price">$5/mo</span>
        <span class="price-label">on Patreon &middot; cancel anytime</span>
      </div>
      <a href="/join/spit-up-society" class="btn btn-primary">Join the Spit-Up Society</a>
    </div>
    <img src="/images/IMG_9055_VSCO.jpeg" alt="Mike and John recording the Dudela Podcast" class="huddle-photo" />
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .huddle {
    padding: var(--space-6) 0;
  }
  .huddle-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .huddle-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-label);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--forest-900);
    background: var(--amber-500);
    padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .huddle h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
    max-width: 14ch;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem;
  }
  .huddle-sub {
    color: var(--text-on-dark-muted);
    max-width: 42ch;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }
  .huddle-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    font-family: var(--font-label);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .huddle-list li {
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
    position: relative;
    color: var(--text-on-dark-muted);
  }
  .huddle-list li::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.55em;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--amber-500);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .huddle-price {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }
  .price {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    color: var(--amber-500);
  }
  .price-label {
    font-family: var(--font-label);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-on-dark-muted);
  }
  .huddle-photo {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: 50% 30%;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }
  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .huddle-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
